    "description": "<strong>基于流行的互联网creepypasta的气氛恐怖游戏。<br><br>游戏邀请您穿越错综复杂的黄色房间迷宫，穿越夜村、废弃办公室和 Backrooms 中的其他危险场所。你只有一个目标——生存并找到出路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217840/extras/2739e5604534d2bdd6c5516b2dd97ecf.poster.avif?t=1696925952\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217840/extras/2739e5604534d2bdd6c5516b2dd97ecf.webm?t=1696925952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217840/extras/2739e5604534d2bdd6c5516b2dd97ecf.mp4?t=1696925952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>“如果你够倒霉，你可能会脱离现实，最终进入 Backrooms，那里除了潮湿的旧地毯、黄色墙纸、无尽的背景噪音、明亮的白光和大约六亿平方英里的臭味之外什么都没有的空房间。<br>如果你听到附近有东西在移动，就跑，因为它一定也听到了你的声音。”<br>你真的需要小心，因为你不是这个奇怪地方的唯一居民。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217840/extras/282f69a65232cc0bbdad70bdb3153696.poster.avif?t=1696925952\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217840/extras/282f69a65232cc0bbdad70bdb3153696.webm?t=1696925952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217840/extras/282f69a65232cc0bbdad70bdb3153696.mp4?t=1696925952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>图形、声音、视觉效果和角色动画尽可能接近《Backrooms》中的原始素材。事实上，这款游戏是一个身临其境的模拟器 - 一个对 Backrooms 世界的互动之旅。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217840/extras/e488ddb084faf5637f4d56250d08630d.poster.avif?t=1696925952\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217840/extras/e488ddb084faf5637f4d56250d08630d.webm?t=1696925952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217840/extras/e488ddb084faf5637f4d56250d08630d.mp4?t=1696925952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
